snippet.title: What Life Is Really Like For Amber Rose Today
snippet.description:
Model and television personality Amber Rose began turning heads when she appeared in Young Jeezy and Kanye West’s music video for “Put On” in 2008. Rose then appeared in a print ad for Louis Vuitton and was soon walking the runways in New York.

She signed with Ford Models in 2009 and became a regular fixture in hip-hop music videos for artists like Wiz Khalifa, Ludacris, and Nicki Minaj. Rose also began pursuing her own projects, which led to her landing a VH1 talk show called The Amber Rose Show.

After years of taking on various projects in the entertainment world and raising a family, Rose has gradually stepped away from the spotlight. Here’s what life is really like for Amber Rose today.
